Name: Mazing
About the game: Mazing is a maze game with different maze genres. Choose your maze genre, complete the maze, and unlock the next maze. The maze becomes bigger and harder. Features 30 Single Levels! 10 Single(Time) Levels! 3 Single(Leaderboard) Levels! 30 Multi Levels! 10 Multi(Time) Levels! 3 Multi(Leaderboard) Levels! Online Levels!
